{"tid":2496721,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉] 一人一個茶記冷知識","createTime":"2021-04-20T04:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T04:38:18.000Z","uid":48520,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"32b82a344e7d7293cd8591b1e24cd48805b299d6","tid":2496721,"uid":48520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"1. 絲襪奶茶係用棉襖布沖。因為棉襖毛布密度高，先唔會漏啲茶渣出嚟。但白色嘅茶袋喺沖完奶茶後會變成淡啡色，所以嗰個年代嘅人就取笑茶袋係絲襪，叫吓叫吓大家都慣咗叫絲襪奶茶<br />\n<br />\n2. 茶記地板常見嘅馬賽克磚（又叫做「紙皮石」），係因為60年代由歐洲入口返嚟好平<br />\n<br />\n3. 炮製港式奶茶口訣「一沖、二焗、三撞、四回溫」"},{"pid":"e7817f44628f276f042992d07ec84b372731ac3d","tid":2496721,"uid":367224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:22:24.000Z","msg":"一乾三濕？"},{"pid":"4657414c988bc545a3b1618d7cb563e419448acf","tid":2496721,"uid":48520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"Fact Check：<br />\n《一對絲襪，一杯奶茶：奶茶流動的故事》"},{"pid":"2efc6f36b3987e3d15c795f6a2e156c58c642acc","tid":2496721,"uid":229601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:22:59.000Z","msg":"奶茶飲到見底先算係尊重水吧師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a48c4a65f3baa0ab17efdc9b4aa4deaa9d5521","tid":2496721,"uid":48520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4657414c988bc545a3b1618d7cb563e419448acf","tid":2496721,"uid":48520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"Fact Check：<br />\n《一對絲襪，一杯奶茶：奶茶流動的故事》"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYjAKkyYjmxg2fHbjLZ2PLQKeDUTKheesEZ5Ps61EchkV?filename=ZnySLXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnySLXG.jpg&h=627cbcc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35223098c2016ee865b3f627481963c4809209e6","tid":2496721,"uid":48520,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7817f44628f276f042992d07ec84b3727