id":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"255da8ff6595f11eeaee70610b4dc27a25c87ba3","tid":2496721,"uid":381750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf95a544a415af3daf84fa175d0fa37946789a7a","tid":2496721,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"大部分茶餐廳沖「茶走」時<br />\n會將匙羹放入杯裡<br />\n而普通奶茶會將匙羹放碟上<br />\n畀伙記易分辨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"我做左咁耐 都未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:29:31.000Z","msg":"巴打做茶記？<br />\n有冇野分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3da370ab93a1def4f68b826136adc93b898a58","tid":2496721,"uid":229601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"255da8ff6595f11eeaee70610b4dc27a25c87ba3","tid":2496721,"uid":381750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf95a544a415af3daf84fa175d0fa37946789a7a","tid":2496721,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"大部分茶餐廳沖「茶走」時<br />\n會將匙羹放入杯裡<br />\n而普通奶茶會將匙羹放碟上<br />\n畀伙記易分辨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"我做左咁耐 都未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"即係唔會特別分茶走同普通奶茶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b261f936aaebf15840b2d022954900165e8c30f5","tid":2496721,"uid":155674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa9b6e1890c7022b403109c1da42e89ce857f720","tid":2496721,"uid":64449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"點解白飯喺靚仔？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:31:41.000Z","msg":"其實，白飯點解叫「靚仔」，乃是源於白粥叫「妹」，其讀音需要變調，音【mui1】。至於點解白粥叫「妹」呢？原因並不是什麼「青靚白靜」，而是由潮州打冷鋪傳過去的。<br />\n<br />\n以前的打冷鋪，裡面的伙計多數是潮州人。他們不會叫冷佬粥做「粥」，而係叫「糜」。「糜」是粥的古叫法，東漢劉熙所撰的《釋名》曰：「糜，煑米使糜爛也」，相傳晉惠帝的名句「何不食肉糜」，「肉糜」便是肉粥的意思。<br />\n<br />\n由於「糜」字在潮州話（及閩南話）的讀音，是【mu&ecirc;】，其讀讀音跟粵語妹妹的「妹」字一樣，於是其他香港人便有樣學樣，跟着冷佬叫粥做「妹」，而妹字在粵語裡，往往又會出現變調的現象，所以便讀成了【mui1】了。<br />\n<br />\n白粥叫「妹（糜）」的講法傳入茶仔之後，便發展出白飯叫「靚仔」的講法"},{"pid":"6bf8dd1ecfb80f851475bf06dd0310c27059ab19","tid":2496721,"uid":381750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f3da370ab93a1def4f68b826136adc93b898a58","tid":2496721,"uid":229601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"255da8ff6595f11eeaee70610b4dc27a25c87ba3","tid":2496721,"uid":381750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf95a544a415af3daf84fa175d0fa37946789a7a","tid":2496721,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"大部分茶餐廳沖「茶走」時<br />\n會將匙羹放入杯裡<br />\n而普通奶茶會將匙羹放碟上<br />\n畀伙記易分辨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"我做左咁耐 都未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"即係唔會特別分茶走同普通奶茶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"其實睇得出 真係有啲分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fef6633097f343e8e3c6eda65018bd040a550db","tid":2496721,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:32:30.000Z","msg":"食環黎果陣 有老鼠要拎碗cup住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" 